---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <BaseHead title={`About - ${SITE_TITLE}`} description={`Learn more about ${SITE_DESCRIPTION}`} />
        <style>
            main {
                width: 960px;
                max-width: calc(100% - 2em);
                margin: auto;
                padding: 3em 1em;
            }
            .content-card {
                background: var(--glass-bg);
                backdrop-filter: blur(var(--glass-blur));
                -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(var(--glass-blur));
                border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
                border-radius: 16px;
                padding: 2em 3em;
                line-height: 1.6;
                box-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            }
            .about-title {
                font-size: 2.5em;
                font-weight: 700;
                margin-bottom: 1em;
                color: var(--black);
            }
            .about-content h2 {
                font-size: 1.8em;
                font-weight: 700;
                margin-top: 2em;
                color: var(--black);
            }
            .about-content p {
                margin-bottom: 1.2em;
                color: #333;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <Header />
        <main>
            <div class="content-card">
                <h1 class="about-title">Our Mission: Finding Your Perfect Sound</h1>
                <div class="about-content">
                    <p>
                        Welcome to BestValueEarbuds, your trusted guide in the crowded world of personal audio. We know that finding the right earbuds, headphones, or speakers can be overwhelming. With countless brands, technical jargon, and fluctuating prices, making a confident choice is harder than ever.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        That’s why we’re here.
                    </p>

                    <h2>Modern | Affordable | Audio</h2>
                    <p>
                        Our philosophy is built on a simple slogan: <strong>Modern, Affordable, Audio.</strong> We believe that everyone deserves access to high-quality sound without breaking the bank. Our mission is to cut through the marketing hype and deliver clear, honest, and expert reviews on audio gear that offers the best possible value.
                    </p>
                    
                    <h2>What We Do</h2>
                    <p>
                        Our team of audio enthusiasts rigorously tests a wide range of sound accessories. We dive deep into what matters most:
                    </p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Sound Quality:</strong> Clarity, bass, and overall audio fidelity.</li>
                        <li><strong>Comfort & Design:</strong> How they feel during long listening sessions.</li>
                        <li><strong>Features & Performance:</strong> Battery life, connectivity, noise cancellation, and microphone quality.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>
                        Every review is independent, unbiased, and written for real-world users. Whether you're a commuter, a fitness enthusiast, a gamer, or an audiophile on a budget, we're here to help you find the perfect gear for your needs.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Thank you for trusting us on your audio journey.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>
        <Footer />
    </body>
</html>
